Village, San Diego Wild Animal Park, Escondido). More than 1,000 lights will 
cast animal silhouettes on the park lagoon. The event will also feature face 
painting and crafts for children. Special admission price of $4.75 for adults, 
$2.50 for children ages 3-15. Participants are asked to bring canned food or 
wrapped gifts to be distributed to needy families. Call 747-8702, Ext. 5140. 
</P>
