<TEXT>
<P>
A team from Torrance won the boys 13 and under South Bay Basketball League 
championship with a 13-1 record. Team members were Dave Brown, Tremaine 
Mayeaux, David Rangel, Doug Francis, John Ohrenberger, Mateo Camargo and Ryan 
Bozof. 
</P>
<P>
