the second consecutive season to the California State Select soccer team for 
girls under 16. 
</P>
<P>
The Cal State Dominguez Hills women's basketball team plays host to Cal State 
Stanislaus Saturday at 7:30 p.m. and the University of La Verne on Tuesday at 
5:45 p.m. The men's team plays at Southern California College in Costa Mesa 
Saturday, plays host to Point Loma Thursday and Northern Colorado Dec. 15. All 
games will be played at 7:30 p.m. 
