Santa Paula City Council elected John A. F. Melton to his fourth one-year term 
as mayor in 16 years. 
</P>
<P>
Melton, a retired area manager for Southern California Edison Co., was 
reelected in November to his fifth four-year term on the City Council and was 
selected to lead the city Monday. 
</P>
<P>
