<HEADLINE>
<P>
SITE OF WHITTIER CHRISTIAN GAME MOVED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Southern Section Division IX football playoff game between Whittier 
Christian and Tehachapi will be played at 7:30 p.m. Saturday at Bakersfield 
College. 
</P>
<P>
The game had been scheduled at Tehachapi High School. 
</P>
<P>
Whittier Christian (12-0) won the Olympic League title with a 9-0 record. 
Tehachapi (12-1) was the Desert Inyo League champion at 9-1. 
</P>
