ERNST &amp; YOUNG (COMPANY); ACCOUNTING; LICENSES; LINCOLN SAVINGS &amp; LOAN 
ASSOCIATION; AMERICAN CONTINENTAL CORP; AUDITS; NEGLIGENCE 
