<HEADLINE>
<P>
FIVE MMEBERS OF CAL STATE LONG BEACH FOOTBALL TEAM SELECTED FOR ALL-STARS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Cal State Long Beach senior linebacker Pepper Jenkins and junior defensive end 
Edward Lair have been named to the All-Big West Conference first team. 
</P>
<P>
