<TEXT>
<P>
Ty Detmer, the third straight junior winner of the Heisman Trophy, claimed his 
award today in New York, saying he'll be back for another season if not for 
another statue. 
</P>
<P>
"We're losing quite a few players," the BYU quarterback said. "We've got a 
young team next year. I'm going to enjoy it now, while it's here." 
</P>
